album.title: I Got Dem Ol' Kozmic Blues Again Mama!

wiki.content:
This song is about hope and trying to see the good in situations, but always seeming to come up short - something that is a common Blues theme. This is one of the songs that showcased Joplin's powerful vocals.

track.name: Kozmic Blues
comments: God!! How I love this amazing song!
always thought that she had some pretty fine bands backing her
wowowow! this is better than all other songs of her which i know!
KOZMIC, yeh thats what it is    kozmic.....
Coming of age and listening to Janis live leaves little that can be said here. A Flame of Spirit that burned too hot and too fast but could not have been otherwise.
That determination in her voice. Wow!
Plenty of girl songslingers have or had a better voice, but what Janis had was the ability to make you FEEL HER PAIN
